### ================== RUTAS CON AUTENTICACIÓN ==================

### Obtener todos los envíos (CON token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ocul/Shipments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener envío por ID (CON token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ocul/Shipments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear un nuevo envío (CON token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ocul/Shipments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id_order": 3,
  "tracking_number": "GHI789JKL012",
  "fecha_envio": "2025-10-16T10:00:00Z",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Actualizar un envío (CON token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/ocul/Shipments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tracking_number": "UPDATEDTRACK9876",
  "status": "SHIPPED"
}

### Eliminar un envío físicamente (CON token)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/ocul/Shipments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Eliminar un envío lógicamente (CON token)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/ocul/Shipments/1/logic
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
